        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Bit more math (probably errant also hehe)</P><P>10 delay = 1 sec</P><P>so<BR>12 delay = 1.2 sec = 50 attacks/minute<BR>18 delay = 1.8 sec = 33.3 attacks/minute</P><P>assuming pets do double attacks for max damage every time, then we get a theoretical max damage ranking of:</P><P>- old pet = 5500 damage/minute<BR>- mage epic pet (79 dam/80% max haste)= 5530 damage/minute<BR>- EoT = 4733 damage/minute<BR>- pre-Luclin EoT = 3796 damage/minute<BR>- lvl 49 pet = 3663 damage/minute</P><P>I could live with that if it wasn't for a minor detail:<BR>mage epic pet = 3500 hps + 50 pts damage shield<BR>EoT = 2350 hps<BR>mobs hitting for 170</P><P>N</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
